textBox.richText: Got the new phone: an HTC thunderbolt. (Something about working the SW on both chips...eat your own breakfast kinda thing...) Had about 6" on the ground when I woke up. Mom and Max were feeling mellow; did one run down cheshire, then ran off on my own. No pioneer or eagle open...those closed down last week. Bunch of bowl laps, including the upper switchyard stuff. Did lower tophers, weather station, and rettas to close the day.
